---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - WFlows"
  description="Learn how WFlows collects, uses, and protects your personal information in accordance with LGPD and GDPR."
>
  <div class="bg-navy-950 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">Last Updated: February 10, 2026</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-300">
          <!-- Introduction -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              1. Introduction
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              VE SOFTWARE ENGINEERING LTDA, doing business as WFlows ("WFlows",
              "we", "us", or "our"), a Brazilian corporation with principal
              place of business at 415 Rua Itabaiana, Vila Velha ES, Brazil
              29102290, is committed to protecting your privacy and personal
              information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use,
              disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our
              website and use our AI-powered revenue and operations systems
              services.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We collect personal data about you such as your name, email
              address, company information, and business requirements when you
              complete forms on our website or contact us for any reason. We may
              also collect additional information if you voluntarily provide it
              during your interactions with us.
            </p>
            <p>
              We monitor website usage including page visits, time spent on
              site, traffic patterns, and location data to help us understand
              our users and improve our services. This information may be
              aggregated or statistical, meaning we cannot identify you
              individually.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Information We Collect -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              2. Information We Collect
            </h2>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-100 mb-3">
              Information you provide directly to us:
            </h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
              <li>
                Contact information (name, email address, phone number, company
                name, job title)
              </li>
              <li>Project requirements and business goals</li>
              <li>Messages and communications through our website forms</li>
              <li>
                Information shared during consultations and strategy calls
              </li>
              <li>
                Business data necessary for service delivery (CRM access,
                workflow information, marketing data)
              </li>
              <li>Payment and billing information</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-100 mb-3">
              Information we collect automatically:
            </h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>
                Website usage data (pages visited, time spent, navigation
                patterns)
              </li>
              <li>
                Technical information (IP address, browser type, device
                information, operating system)
              </li>
              <li>Analytics data to improve website performance</li>
              <li>Cookies and similar tracking technologies</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- How We Use Your Information -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              3. How We Use Your Information
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We use your personal information for the following purposes:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>
                To provide our automated outbound, inbound capture, RevOps, and
                operations automation services
              </li>
              <li>
                To communicate with you about projects and respond to inquiries
              </li>
              <li>
                To understand your business needs and deliver customized
                solutions
              </li>
              <li>
                To configure and maintain AI workflows and automation systems
              </li>
              <li>To improve our website and service offerings</li>
              <li>To send marketing communications (with your consent)</li>
              <li>To comply with legal obligations and protect our rights</li>
              <li>
                For administrative purposes and maintaining client relationships
              </li>
              <li>
                To analyze system performance and optimize automation workflows
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- Marketing Communications -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              4. Marketing Communications
            </h2>
            <p>
              We may contact you via email, phone, mail, or other methods about
              our services that may interest you, unless you have opted out. You
              can unsubscribe from marketing communications at any time by
              following the instructions in our emails or contacting us at <a
                href="mailto:contact@wflows.ai"
                class="text-teal-400 hover:text-teal-300">contact@wflows.ai</a
              >.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Information Sharing -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              5. Information Sharing
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We do not sell your personal information to third parties. We may
              share your information only in the following circumstances:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>
                <strong>Service providers:</strong> With trusted providers who help
                us operate our website and business (hosting, analytics, email services,
                payment processors)
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>AI and automation platforms:</strong> With third-party platforms
                necessary for service delivery (Clay, HubSpot, Make.com, n8n, Instantly,
                Retell AI, Vapi, and other tools specified in your service agreement)
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Contractors:</strong> With trusted contractors who assist
                with project delivery under strict confidentiality agreements
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Legal requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect
                our rights and safety
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Business transfers:</strong> In connection with a business
                transfer or merger
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4">
              All third parties are required to keep your information
              confidential and use it only for specified purposes.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Data Security -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              6. Data Security
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal
              information, including:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Secure hosting with reputable providers</li>
              <li>Access controls limiting who can view your information</li>
              <li>Regular security updates and monitoring</li>
              <li>Encrypted connections for data transmission (SSL/TLS)</li>
              <li>Secure API integrations with automation platforms</li>
              <li>Regular security audits of our systems</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4">
              While we strive to protect your data, no internet transmission is
              completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Your Rights and Choices -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              7. Your Rights and Choices
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              You have the following rights regarding your personal information:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>
                <strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of the personal information
                we hold about you
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Correction:</strong> Ask us to update or correct inaccurate
                information
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Deletion:</strong> Request that we delete your personal information
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Opt-out:</strong> Unsubscribe from marketing communications
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Restriction:</strong> Limit how we process your information
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Portability:</strong> Receive your data in machine-readable
                format (where applicable)
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Withdraw consent:</strong> Withdraw previously given consent
                at any time
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4">
              To exercise these rights, contact us at <a
                href="mailto:contact@wflows.ai"
                class="text-teal-400 hover:text-teal-300">contact@wflows.ai</a
              >. We will respond within 30 days.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Cookies and Tracking Technologies -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              8. Cookies and Tracking Technologies
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4">We use cookies and similar technologies to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Remember your preferences and improve user experience</li>
              <li>Analyze website traffic and visitor behavior</li>
              <li>Measure marketing effectiveness</li>
              <li>Provide relevant content</li>
              <li>Track conversion events</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4">
              You can control cookies through your browser settings, though
              disabling cookies may affect website functionality.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Data Retention -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              9. Data Retention
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We retain your information for as long as necessary to:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
              <li>Provide our services and maintain business relationships</li>
              <li>
                Comply with legal requirements (including Brazilian tax and
                business record laws)
              </li>
              <li>Resolve disputes</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-100 mb-3">
              Specific retention periods:
            </h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Contact and project data: 7 years for business records</li>
              <li>Marketing data: Until you unsubscribe or request deletion</li>
              <li>Website analytics: Aggregated data retained indefinitely</li>
              <li>
                Service delivery data: Duration of service agreement plus 7
                years
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- Third-Party Services and Integrations -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              10. Third-Party Services and Integrations
            </h2>
            <p>
              Our services involve integration with third-party platforms (CRM
              systems, marketing automation tools, AI platforms). We are not
              responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties. We
              recommend reviewing their privacy policies.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Children's Privacy -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              11. Children's Privacy
            </h2>
            <p>
              Our services are not intended for individuals under 18 years of
              age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from
              children under 16.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- International Data Transfers -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              12. International Data Transfers
            </h2>
            <p>
              Your information may be transferred to and processed in countries
              outside Brazil, including the United States and European Union,
              where our service providers and automation platforms operate. We
              ensure appropriate protections are in place for such transfers in
              compliance with LGPD (Brazilian General Data Protection Law) and
              GDPR requirements.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- LGPD Rights (Brazilian Residents) -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              13. LGPD Rights (Brazilian Residents)
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              If you are in Brazil, you have rights under the Lei Geral de
              Proteção de Dados (LGPD), including:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Confirmation of the existence of processing</li>
              <li>Access to your data</li>
              <li>Correction of incomplete, inaccurate, or outdated data</li>
              <li>
                Anonymization, blocking, or deletion of unnecessary or excessive
                data
              </li>
              <li>Portability of data to another service provider</li>
              <li>Deletion of data processed with your consent</li>
              <li>
                Information about public and private entities with which we
                share data
              </li>
              <li>
                Information about the possibility of denying consent and the
                consequences
              </li>
              <li>Revocation of consent</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4">
              To exercise these rights, contact our Data Protection Officer at <a
                href="mailto:contact@wflows.ai"
                class="text-teal-400 hover:text-teal-300">contact@wflows.ai</a
              >.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- GDPR Rights (EU Residents) -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              14. GDPR Rights (EU Residents)
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              If you are in the European Union, you have additional rights under
              GDPR:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
              <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
              <li>
                Data portability (receive your data in machine-readable format)
              </li>
              <li>Lodge complaints with data protection authorities</li>
              <li>Right to be forgotten (erasure of personal data)</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- Changes to This Policy -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              15. Changes to This Policy
            </h2>
            <p>
              We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify you
              of material changes by posting the updated policy on our website
              and sending email notification to registered users. Your continued
              use of our services constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Contact Information -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
              16. Contact Information
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              For questions about this Privacy Policy or to exercise your
              rights, contact us at:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-navy-900/50 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-100 mb-2">
                VE SOFTWARE ENGINEERING LTDA (WFlows)
              </p>
              <p>
                Email: <a
                  href="mailto:contact@wflows.ai"
                  class="text-teal-400 hover:text-teal-300">contact@wflows.ai</a
                >
              </p>
              <p>
                Website: <a
                  href="https://wflows.ai"
                  class="text-teal-400 hover:text-teal-300">wflows.ai</a
                >
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Back to Home -->
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-800">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-flex items-center text-teal-400 hover:text-teal-300 transition-colors"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 mr-2"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path>
          </svg>
          Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
